data.description: MLS# 266395 Welcome home to this spacious 2-story located in Riverview Pointe, a quiet neighborhood tucked in between the best of Tri-Cities amenities! You will find great curb appeal and room to grow with this 1904 sq ft home. Enjoy an inviting living room with gas fireplace, dining area just off the kitchen with enough space for all your special gatherings, and a kitchen that features beautiful wood cabinetry, pantry and island/breakfast bar. You will love the tile and laminate floors that flow through the main living areas. There are 4 bedrooms, and 2.5 bathrooms, including an owner’s suite with a walk-in closet, and private bath. If you’re looking for storage and room for your upcoming spring projects, this home has plenty with a 3 car garage. The outdoor areas are just as inviting, spend your leisure time on your back patio, enjoying the lovely landscaping, and private fenced yard. You can’t beat the location of this home, just a short distance to the community park, with shopping, restaurants, medical, and freeway access, just down the street.
